            <h3 class="pb-2">Our Solution</h3>
            <p>At TVSensei, we create lessons that redefine the purpose of TV.</p>
            <p>Our users don’t simply sit back and enjoy the show, they: </p>
            <p>1. Do targeted listening and practice exercises with key vocabulary and phrases</p> <p></p>
            <p>2. Create, speak, and record dialogues as if they were the main character, and </p> <p></p>
            <p>3. Share in the target language about what they watched with watch buddies.</p> <p></p>
            <p>When you watch on TVSensei, you’re an active learner when it counts–completing exercises and more–and a passive learner when it doesn’t. We guide you in how you view, so watching TV can have relaxing and engaging moments–just like a well written show.</p>
